    {
      "id": "18d4750c-f3ba-808f-9421-dcc833616c8e",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "KT analyzes historical records to infer students’ knowledge states, and deep learning methods are the current state-of-the-art. However, the current techniques tend to treat records as a single time-series AND they don’t account for possible correlations. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "18d4750c-f3ba-808f-9421-dcc833616c8e",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
