    {
      "id": "18d4750c-f3ba-80fb-93bf-f23edab9e140",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors propose Multi-Granularity Ensemble Interaction Graph Modeling for Knowledge Tracing which is meant to address the two constraints. Analysis on four datasets show that the model outperforms other approaches.",
